'''菲爾角銀光魚'''（{{lang-en|'''Cape Fear shiner'''}}，[[學名|學名]]：'''''Notropis mekistocholas'''''），又名'''菲爾角美洲鱥'''，是[[鯉科|鯉科]]的一種小型[[淡水魚|淡水魚]]，原産於[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]中央數縣，也僅見於[[菲爾角河|菲爾角河]]盆地的淺溪中。魚體呈黃色，沿中線兩側各有一條黑色條紋，魚唇也是黑色的。菲爾角銀光魚常常與其他的小鰷魚混在一起遊動，每年可產兩次卵，野生條件下壽命為二至三年。雌雄兩性外表基本相同，但繁殖季節體色會發生變化。1962年被發現。

菲爾角銀光魚本身數量較少，建築大壩和水污染等造成的棲息地破壞更是雪上加霜。1987年被首次認定為瀕危物種，雖然已經開始對次物種進行保護，其現依然已是[[極危物種|極危物種]]，野生條件下約只有五條菲爾角銀光魚。

== 命名法==

菲爾角銀光魚在1962年首次被發現，<ref name="Hewitt">{{cite journal| last =Hewitt| first =Amanda| coauthors =W. Gregory Cope, Thomas J. Kwak, Tom Augspurger, Peter R. Lazaro, and Damian Shea| title =Influence of water quality and associated contaminants on survival and growth of the endangered Cape Fear shiner (Notropis mekistocholas)| journal =Environmental Toxicology and Chemistry| volume =25| issue =9| pages =2288–98| publisher =SETAC Press| date =2006-03-16| url =http://www4.ncsu.edu/~tkwak/Hewitt_et_al_2006.pdf| format =PDF| accessdate =2007-12-09| doi =10.1897/05-569R.1| pmid =16986782| archive-date =2007-08-24| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070824073124/http://www4.ncsu.edu/~tkwak/Hewitt_et_al_2006.pdf| dead-url =no}}</ref>1971年被小弗蘭克林（Franklin F. Snelson, Jr.）誤認為新物種。<ref name="Rabon"/>其學名來自[[古希臘語|古希臘語]]mēkistos/μηκιστος（最長/最高或很長，即mēkos/μηκος的最高級）和cholas/χολας（腸子或膽汁）。<ref name="Liddell 1980">{{cite book | author = [[Henry_George_Liddell|Liddell, Henry George]] and [[Robert_Scott_(philologist)|Robert Scott]] | year = 1980 | title = [[A_Greek-English_Lexicon|A Greek-English Lexicon]] (Abridged Edition) | publisher = [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]] | location = United Kingdom | isbn = 0-19-910207-4}}</ref>菲爾角銀光魚屬於[[鯉科|鯉科]] <ref>Gimenez Dixon, M. 1996. [http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/14888/all Notropis mekistocholas].  [http://www.iucnredlist.org 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. ] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6137CKTqL?url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/ |date=20110819073403 |dateformat=iso }} Downloaded on 19 July 2007.</ref>[[美洲鱥屬|美洲鱥屬]]，該屬下包含許多北美鰷魚。它在美洲鱥屬算是一個獨特的物種，因為其腸子狹長而構造更為複雜，同屬生物中只有''Notropis nubilus''有類似特徵。<ref name="Page">{{Cite book | last = Page | first = Lawrence M. | coauthors = Brooks M. Burr | title = A Field Guide to Freshwater Fishes of North America North of Mexico | publisher = Houghton Mifflin Company | year = 1991 | location = Boston | pages = 152–153| isbn = 978-0-395-91091-7}}</ref>而原因主要取決於其素食性。<ref name="Rabon">{{cite web| last = Rabon| first = David| title = Cape Fear Shiner (Notropis mekistocholas)| publisher = US Fish and Wildlife Service| date = 2006-09-25| url = http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/cfshiner.html| accessdate = 2007-12-09| archive-date = 2007-12-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071201005916/http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/cfshiner.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>其魚唇、頭部的形狀及八個[[臀鰭|臀鰭]]鰭條也與衆不同。<ref name="Snelson">{{cite journal| last =Snelson, Jr.| first =Franklin F.| title =Notropis mekistocholas, a New Herbivorous Cyprinid Fish Endemic to the Cape Fear River Basin, North Carolina| journal =Copeia| volume =1971| issue =3| pages =449–462| publisher =American Society of Ichthyologists and Herpetologists| date =1971-09-03| url =http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/es/Snelson_Copeia_1971(3)449-462.pdf| format =PDF| doi =10.2307/1442441| accessdate =2007-12-13| jstor =1442441| archive-date =2007-05-09| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070509042619/http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/es/Snelson_Copeia_1971(3)449-462.pdf| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Pottern">{{Cite news| last =Pottern| first =Gerald| title =The Cape Fear Shiner-One of NC’s Rarest Native Fish| newspaper =The Raleigh Aquarium Society| pages =2–3| year =2007| date =August| url =http://raleighaquariumsociety.org/newsletter/2007/aug2007.pdf| postscript =<!--None-->| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080724025922/http://raleighaquariumsociety.org/newsletter/2007/aug2007.pdf| archivedate =2008-07-24}}</ref>此外，它也是少數擁有[[腹膜|腹膜]]的美洲鱥屬魚類。<ref name="Page"/>與''Notropis procne''及''Notropis stramineus''有親緣關係。<ref name="Snelson"/>

== 描述==
菲爾角銀光魚是一種小型而強壯的魚，體長平均為{{convert|5|cm}}，最大不過{{convert|7.7|cm}}。<ref name="Fact1">{{cite web| last = Rabon| first = David| title = Cape Fear Shiner| publisher = US Fish and Wildlife Service| url = http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/CFS_Fact_Sheet1.pdf| format = PDF| accessdate = 2007-12-09| date = May 2004| archive-date = 2007-05-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070509035612/http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/CFS_Fact_Sheet1.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>體側呈現銀黃色光澤，兩側各有一條黑色條紋橫貫全身直至尾柄，上部還有另外一對條紋，但色澤極為黯淡。<ref name="Atlas">{{cite web| title = Cape Fear Shiner (Notropis mekistocholas)| publisher = North Carolina Atlas of Freshwater Mussels and Endangered Freshwater Fish| url = http://www.wildlife.state.nc.us/pg07_WildlifeSpeciesCon/pg7b1b1_1.htm| accessdate = 2007-12-09| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060925004444/http://www.wildlife.state.nc.us/pg07_WildlifeSpeciesCon/pg7b1b1_1.htm| archivedate =2006-09-25| deadurl = yes}}</ref>鱗屑的輪廓為黑色。<ref name="Page"/>魚鰭略呈黃色，有斑點。<ref name="Page"/>背鰭開始於腹鰭稍靠後的位置。<ref name="Page"/>繁殖季節雄性會變成金色，而雌性則會變成銀色。<ref name="Fact1"/>上唇為黑色，下唇有一條黑色的條紋。<ref name="Rabon"/>

與其他雜食性的同類一樣，菲爾角銀光魚只有[[咽頭齒|咽頭齒]]用以咀嚼食物。<ref name="Zoo">{{cite web| last =Groves| first =John| title =Cape Fear Shiner Conservation & Research| publisher =North Carolina Zoo| url =http://www.nczoo.org/conservationresearch/instate_capefearshiner.cfm| accessdate =2007-12-09| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20071216045427/http://www.nczoo.org/conservationresearch/instate_capefearshiner.cfm| archivedate =2007-12-16| deadurl =yes}}</ref>菲爾角銀光魚的臀鰭有八個鰭條。<ref name="Pottern"/>因為身體略微透明，其盤曲的腸子和黑色腹膜可以直接從體外看到。<ref name="Page1998">{{cite book| last=Page| first=Lawrence M| coauthors=Brooks M Burr| title=A Field Guide to Freshwater Fishes: North America North of Mexico | publisher =Houghton Mifflin Field Guides | year=1998| pages=152| url =http://books.google.com/?id=dSGwawxZJYcC&pg=PA152&dq=Cape+Fear+Shiner| isbn = 0-395-91091-9}}</ref>

== 分佈與棲息地 ==
[[File:CFSRockyRiver1.jpg|thumb]]

菲爾角銀光魚原産於[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]山地地區的[[菲爾角河|菲爾角河]]上盆地。<ref name="Rabon"/>作為美洲鱥屬分佈範圍最狹窄的物種，<ref name="Page"/>現已知只有五個存活的野生種生活在[[查塔姆縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|查塔姆縣]]、[[哈尼特縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|哈尼特縣]]、[[李縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|李縣]]、[[穆爾縣_(北卡羅萊納州)|穆爾縣]]和[[蘭道夫縣_(北卡羅來納州)|蘭道夫縣]]的深河（Deep River）、山楂河（Haw River）和洛磯河（Rocky River）。<ref name="Fact1"/>冬季會從主河道的淺灘遷徙到小型支流里。<ref name="Atlas"/>

其棲息的淺灘多是鵝卵石底，且周圍有[[美國水柳|美國水柳]]和水草為其提供藏身之地。<ref name="Rabon"/>菲爾角銀光魚很少進入水深超過{{convert|0.5|m|ft}}的河流中。<ref name=" Malindzak ">{{cite journal| author = Edward George Malindzak| title = Behavior and habitat use of introduced flathead catfish in a North Carolina Piedmont river| date = 2006-04-21| url = http://www.lib.ncsu.edu/theses/available/etd-06042006-143746/unrestricted/etd.pdf| format = pdf| accessdate = 2007-12-12}}{{dead link|date=十月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>

==習性 ==

菲爾角銀光魚常和其他鰷魚群一起遊動，<ref name="Rabon"/>一般在人工飼養的情況下可以存活六年，但野生情況下只有二到三年的壽命。<ref name="Fact1"/>

根據腸子的構造，菲爾角銀光魚主要以植物為食，但後來有研究發現其也會使用動物性食物。<ref name="Zoo"/>主要食譜包括岩屑、浮游生物、[[硅藻|硅藻]]和其他藻類。

其天敵包括[[莓鱸|莓鱸]]等鱸魚，以及引入的[[鏟鮰|鏟鮰]]。<ref name="Rabon"/>不過成年的鏟鮰因與菲爾角銀光魚棲息地不同而不會對其構成威脅。<ref name=" Malindzak "/>

菲爾角銀光魚在每年5月15日左右水溫{{convert|19|C|F}}時開始產卵。<ref name="Atlas"/>第二次繁殖季通常發生在夏末。<ref name="Fact1"/>兩性的體色在此時發生變化，雄魚的體前側將長出小瘤。<ref name="Atlas"/>產卵時前往洛磯河水流緩慢的區域。幼魚在三天後就會孵化出來，另外還會攜帶五天的[[卵黃囊|卵黃囊]]。<ref name="Fact2">{{cite web| title = Cape Fear Shiner (Notropis mekistocholas)| publisher = US Fish and Wildlife Service| url = http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/CFS_Fact_Sheet2.pdf| format = PDF| accessdate = 2007-12-09| date = May 2005| archive-date = 2007-05-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070509022200/http://www.fws.gov/nc-es/fish/CFS_Fact_Sheet2.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>直到一年之後成熟為止，幼魚會繼續生活在這些水流緩慢的地區。<ref name="Rabon"/>

== 保護==
[[File:Carbonton_Dam.jpg|thumb]]

雖然只有五條野生種，但其人工飼養的數量有1500到3000條。<ref name="Rabon"/>根據美國1973年頒佈的[[瀕危物種法案|瀕危物種法案]]，1987年9月25日菲爾角銀光魚被認定為關鍵棲息地瀕危（Endangered with Critical Habitat）。而自此以後，其數量和棲息地範圍就開始不斷縮小。<ref name="Rabon"/>根據[[雷斯法案|雷斯法案]]，這種魚被限制捕撈或交易。不過據信菲爾角銀光魚在歷史上曾經數量很多。<ref name="Zoo"/>

其生存的主要威脅之一是菲爾角河上的大壩，這些大壩導致這種魚棲息的淺灘消失。一些地理分隔種的消失可能還要歸因於基因問題，不過2004年的研究顯示其遺傳多樣性依然很豐富。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Saillant E, Patton JC, Ross KE, Gold JR |title=Conservation genetics and demographic history of the endangered Cape Fear shiner (Notropis mekistocholas) |journal=Mol. Ecol. |volume=13 |issue=10 |pages=2947–2958 |pmid=15367111 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-294X.2004.02303.x |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-ecology_2004-10_13_10/page/2947|date=October 2004}}</ref>此外水污染也是其瀕危的元兇之一，<ref name="Rabon"/>因為這種魚對污染物十分敏感。<ref name="Hewitt"/>

[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美國魚類及野生動物管理局]]負責菲爾角銀光魚的保護工作。他們已採取了必要的保育措施，1989年捐贈16,000美元以維護[[北卡羅來納動物園|北卡羅來納動物園]]中生活的菲爾角銀光魚。<ref name="Zoo"/>自從1997年成功地進行了人工繁殖以來，這種魚開始變得極易飼養。2001年的一項實驗中，900條菲爾角銀光魚被放生以測試水質。<ref name="Hewitt"/>

2006年2月破壞了菲爾角銀光魚棲息地的Carbonton Dam被拆除，因此其所在河段的水位已恢復歷史正常水平。<ref name="NCWRCa">{{cite web | title =Cape Fear Shiner | publisher =N.C. Wildlife Resources Commission | date =2013 | url =http://www.ncwildlife.org/Learning/Species/Fish/CapeFearShiner.aspx | accessdate =2013-04-24 | archive-date =2013-04-18 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130418122342/http://www.ncwildlife.org/Learning/Species/Fish/CapeFearShiner.aspx | dead-url =no }}</ref>

